{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"jQuery","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/jQuery","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>jQuery 是專精於簡化 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/DOM\">DOM</a>、<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/AJAX\">AJAX</a>、與 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/event\">Event</a> 操作的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\">函式庫</a>。</p>\n<p>jQuery 用 <code>$(selector).action()</code> 格式，指派元素到指定的事件。詳細來說， <code>$(selector)</code> 會呼叫 jQuery 選取 <code>selector</code> 元素，並指派它到稱作 <code>.action()</code> 事件的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ready</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">hide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>上面這段 jQuery 程式碼，會執行與這段原生 JavaScript 程式碼相同的事情：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>display <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>或這段：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>display <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入理解","title":"深入理解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知識","title":"基本知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科的 <a title=\"jQuery\" href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jQuery</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jQuery 官方網站</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術資訊","title":"技術資訊","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://api.jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">API 參考文件</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"深入理解","id":"深入理解"}],"summary":"jQuery 是專精於簡化 DOM、AJAX、與 Event 操作的 JavaScript 函式庫。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"jQuery","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/jquery","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/jquery/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/jQuery","title":"jQuery"}],"pageTitle":"jQuery - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}